3
00:00:05.160 --> 00:00:07.330 
Super sencillo, en inglés usamos una

4
00:00:07.340 --> 00:00:11.030 
palabra que nunca cambia, must, must.

5
00:00:11.040 --> 00:00:17.710 
Por ejemplo, debes tener tu casco, you

6
00:00:17.720 --> 00:00:25.530 
must wear a helmet, debes usar casco, you
must wear a helmet.

7
